  <Summary>No Grave Can Hold Me!: Istvan is haunted by the ghost of Zenna Prohl who he accused of being a witch so he could get her land.

Mission Supernatural: Leftenant Jordan's ghost still flies the foggy skies over England looking for his landing strip.

The Sorrow of the Spirits!: Conrad Ganges has found a way to see the spirit world and to communicate with its inhabitants.

Enter the Ghost!: Winters is an actor performing a play forbidden in the town.  Lord Boynton has sworn to return from the grave to kill anyone attempting to mount the play.

Galleon of Death: Two treasure hunters try to find a sunken galley but run into a ghostly galleon instead.

Lantern in the Rain!: Did the ghost of John Logan flash his ghostly signal lantern to stop Luke Brownell from crashing his train?

The Ghost Battalions: Groups of soldiers have been disappearing into thin air all throughout history.  Did Shelby's men suffer the same fate?

</Summary>
